snippet.title: Eastshade Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Eastshade is an open-world adventure game where you play as a traveling artist and will be released for PC on February 13, 2019 and consoles soon to follow. Wishlist it at http://store.steampowered.com/app/715560

Official Website - http://www.eastshade.com/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/eastshade
